<plot>This film takes a look at life on the Choctaw Native American Reservation in Mississippi. It takes a glimpse at how the Choctaw have gone from one of the poorest tribes in the nation to one of the wealthiest tribes in the span of 10 years. Through this time of economic development the Choctaw have still maintained their strong culture and language.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?653572</url></doc>
